The paper discusses the potential applications of blockchain technology in distributed control and cooperative robotics, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). It also addresses the issue of security and distributed communication, which are relevant to the sub-categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), systems and control (cs.SY), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
